@startuml 21-ask-followups
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Ask Follow-Up Chips

actor User
participant "AskModePage" as UI
participant "POST /api/ask (SSE)" as API
participant "IChatClient" as CC

... streaming answer + citations (flows 19, 20) ...
API -> CC: CompleteAsync\n(non-stream, ask for 3 followups)
CC --> API: JSON ["q1","q2","q3"]
API --> UI: event: followups\ndata: ["q1","q2","q3"]
UI -> UI: render up to 3 FollowUpChip\nunder "FOLLOW-UP" label
UI --> User: chips visible
API --> UI: event: done

User -> UI: tap chip "Draft pitch to Sarah"
UI -> UI: submit("Draft pitch to Sarah")
note right of UI
  Enters flow 19 again
  for the new user turn
end note

@enduml
